                                                        <p class="text-justify">We welcome all the new entrants to this place of education in Vaageswari College of Pharmacy, which is proven in pursuing outcome-based education for developing the overall personality of the students. In the present scenario of modern globalization, the Pharmaceutical education has come to occupy the center stage. In our institution we are very much concerned about the Pharmacy education and co-curriculum and extra curriculum activities of the student with the encouragement of highly qualified faculty members to build up young community Pharmacist. The college has made enormous improvements since its inception and is rated as a one of the best Pharmacy College in Karimnagar District. Incubation center in our institution is providing facilities to all the students, to development the API moieties and converted into novel formulations for the betterment of public health. The placement scenario is quite laudable as many reputed companies visit our campus to recruit the students. I am confident that our alumni is the bench mark of our achievements which make everyone of us feel proud in India and abroad.</p>
